details open=\"\"><summary>Metody</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/appendChild\"><code>appendChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/cloneNode\"><code>cloneNode()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/compareDocumentPosition\"><code>compareDocumentPosition()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/contains\"><code>contains()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/getRootNode\"><code>getRootNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/hasChildNodes\"><code>hasChildNodes()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/insertBefore\"><code>insertBefore()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isDefaultNamespace\"><code>isDefaultNamespace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isEqualNode\"><code>isEqualNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSameNode\"><code>isSameNode()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/isSupported\"><code>isSupported()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupNamespaceURI\"><code>lookupNamespaceURI()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Node/lookupPrefix\"><code>lookupPrefix()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/normalize\"><code>normalize()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/removeChild\"><code>removeChild()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/Node/replaceChild\"><code>replaceChild()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\">\n </div>\n<div id=\"sect2\">\n &nbsp;</div>\n<div id=\"sect3\">\n <span style=\"font-size: 2.14285714285714rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -1px; line-height: 30px;\">Podsumowanie</span></div>\n<p>Zwraca wartość bieżącego węzła.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>wartość</var> = document.nodeValue\n</pre>\n<p><code>wartość</code> to ciąg znaków reprezentujący wartość elementu, jeśli taka istnieje.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"uwagi","title":"Uwagi","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dla dokumentu <code>nodeValue</code> zwraca <code>null</code>. Dla węzłów tekstowych, komentarzy i CDATA <code>nodeValue</code> zwraca zawartość węzła. Dla węzłów atrybutów, zwracana jest wartość atrybutu.</p>\n<p>Poniższa tabela przedstawia wartości zwracane dla różnych interfejsów:</p>\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th class=\"header\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Interfejs</th>\n   <th class=\"header\" style=\"text-align: center;\">nodeValue</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Attr</td>\n   <td>wartość atrybutu</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>CDATASection</td>\n   <td>treść sekcji CDATA</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Comment</td>\n   <td>treść komentarza</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Document</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>DocumentFragment</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>DocumentType</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Element</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>NamedNodeMap</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>EntityReference</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Notation</td>\n   <td>null</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>ProcessingInstruction</td>\n   <td>cała treść, wyłączając cel</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Text</td>\n   <td>treść węzła tekstowego</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>Jeśli <code>nodeValue</code> z definicji ma wartość <code>null</code>, ustawianie tej właściwości nie będzie mieć efektu.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacja","title":"Specyfikacja","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/2000/REC-DOM-Level-2-Core-20001113/core.html#ID-F68D080\" rel=\" noopener\">nodeValue </a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Składnia","id":"sk.c5.82adnia"},{"text":"Uwagi","id":"uwagi"},{"text":"Specyfikacja","id":"specyfikacja"}],"summary":"Zwraca wartość bieżącego węzła.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Node.nodeValue","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Node.nodeValue","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Node.nodeValue","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"element.nodeValue","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Node.nodeValue","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Node.nodeValue","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Node.nodeValue","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/api/node/nodevalue","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/api/node/nodevalu